<l>yāveṉ viṉāvi ṉaiye ṉiṟutiyu</l>
<l>māyiya ṟiriyā teṉmaṉār pulava</l>
<l>rāvayiṉ vakara maiyoṭuṅ keṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Words which] begin with a demonstrative and end in <foreign xml:lang="ta">-ai</foreign></l>
<l>will approximately appear having combined with <foreign xml:lang="ta">vaṟṟu.</foreign><note place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">avaiyaṟṟai.</foreign> The <foreign xml:lang="ta">v</foreign> of <foreign xml:lang="ta">vaṟṟu</foreign> is removed by rule 123.</note></l>
      </lg>
